Helpers
-------

The *helpers* ususally are modules that hold functionality cross to the whole application.
Helpers are plugged-in to Cuba app and are globally accessible.

**Example**

    # ./app.rb
    # ...some of your code
    Cuba.plugin UserHelpers
    # ...more of your code


    # helpers/user_helper.rb
    module UserHelpers
      def current_user
        authenticated(User)
      end
    end

